{"tid":1451934,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"葵芳地鐵站可能有殘留山埃，如非必要香港市民請勿前往。","createTime":"2019-08-11T22:07:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T01:13:32.000Z","uid":290949,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b760861a26b9eeaf0b30053d94ecddb0d49cda02","tid":1451934,"uid":290949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T22:07:51.000Z","msg":"轉貼：<br />\n[請廣傳，出自醫學院博士的緊急通知] <br />\n葵芳地鐵站可能有殘留山埃，如非必要香港市民請勿前往。<br />\n<br />\n警察於8月11日，葵芳地鐵站發射疑似過期催淚彈，會釋放出氧化山埃 (Cyanide Oxides)，可經皮膚及呼吸道吸收。<br />\n如該化學物經呼吸系列入，與水份作化學作用會變成氫化山埃 (Hydrogen Cyanide)，是納粹當年大規模殺害猶太人之最有效毒藥。<br />\n由於地鐵室內空間尤其不通風，毒素會殘留在地鐵站建築物內部。所有人士，特別是長者、孕婦、小孩，長期病患及呼吸疾病人士，更應遠離該地鐵站，直至港鐵完成毒理化驗，證實安全為止。"},{"pid":"4606883029073d4818f111b9ecfeae5909f273f3","tid":1451934,"uid":275074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T22:21:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f5015deb12ee6098c1d72ed4fdba74fcde472958","tid":1451934,"uid":261470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T22:38:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f32065c6ae6e2d3318397cbee526674c65f12f4c","tid":1451934,"uid":140438,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T23:25:49.000Z","msg":"頭先入過地鐵站，無乜味"},{"pid":"b7ef4c22a51ea463dca4345d6af100c9b02b1f34","tid":1451934,"uid":6506,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"f32065c6ae6e2d3318397cbee526674c65f12f4c","tid":1451934,"uid":140438,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T23:25:49.000Z","msg":"頭先入過地鐵站，無乜味"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T23:26:58.000Z","msg":"山埃係無味<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa62e27e943e832c0955ed9bec1b04c6f098e2f2","tid":1451934,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T01:13:32.000Z","msg":"乜撚嘢氫化山埃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係氰化, 山埃化氫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n明明自己都識打, Hydrogen Cyanide, 唔係Nitrile Hydride<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}